messages.message: Update for people following this thread: Issue has been resolved! There was an ibannotator project pinned to an earlier version (0.0.7) of ib_layout_lm_trainer, where predictions were being stored in task data. It's now pointing to a current version of the trainer lib
@arun sounds great!  thank you for following through.  Can we write a PM so that we can discuss in the incident review meeting.
